|-----------|-----------|-------------------|
| `overview-view.ts` | Dashboard (Feed) | Compact hero -> scrollable card/bento grid |
| `usage-view.ts` | Dashboard (Feed) | Compact hero -> scrollable card grid |
| `memory-view.ts` | Dashboard (Feed) | Compact hero -> stat cards -> searchable card grid |
| `security-view.ts` | Dashboard (Feed) | Compact hero -> scrollable card grid |
