## Required States (All Views)

Every view must handle all three states — never show a blank screen:

1. **Loading**: skeleton placeholders matching final layout shape
2. **Populated**: full content with realistic data
3. **Error**: inline error banner with retry action + `<hu-toast>` for transient errors

## Rules

- Conversation views: conversation area MUST be primary (`flex: 1`), controls MUST anchor to bottom
- All views: content occupies minimum 60% of viewport; controls defer to content
- Responsive: verify behavior at all 4 breakpoints (480px sm, 640px md, 768px lg, 1024px xl)
- Consult `docs/standards/design/visual-standards.md` quality checklist (section 10) before shipping
